Cleaning up the storage from the pet shelter... to the left a #vaccine needle (0.7x19mm), to the right a #microchip needle (2.6x40mm).
The chip that fits in there does not have a battery so it can only be scanned from 3-8 cm, not tracked via GPS.
Pen for scale.
